s Fan Appz serves as well as the products and services Fan Appz provides</li><li>Update on a timely basis the Fan Appz CRM system with accurate customer and pipeline information.</li><li>Timely complete administrative tasks such as expense reports</li></ul><p><strong>Education and Qualifications/ Skills and Competencies</strong></p><ul><li>Requires 5+ years of experience in software sales in a direct account ownership role</li><li>Demonstrated history of achieving sales quota of $2M+ of annual revenue</li><li>Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree Preferred</li><li>Ability to prospect and close deals</li><li>Experience selling software applications to Fortune 1000 Companies and C level executives</li><li>Team player with strong interpersonal&nbsp; and communication skills.</li><li>Excellent negotiating and closing skills with prospects and customers.</li><li>Travel may be needed.<br />&nbsp;</li></ul><p>Fan Appz does not accept unsolicited headhunter and agency resumes. Fan Appz will not pay fees to any third-party agency or company that does not have a signed agreement with the Company.</p>]]></description>
