			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Fan Appz is seeking world class sales professionals to join a dynamic team dedicated to leading the next generation of social media marketing platforms.</p>
<p>
<strong>Fan Appz Overview</strong><br />
Fan Appz solutions are used by many of the world&rsquo;s largest brands to harness the power of social media to acquire new customers and maximize the lifetime value of their fans.&nbsp; The company provides a set of &ldquo;cloud based&rdquo; applications accessible over the Internet that enables its customers to do the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>
Build and grow a social media audience across Facebook, Twitter and other social media platforms</li>
<li>
Drive reach and engagement through Fan Appz applications which publish to social media platforms and provide fan interaction opportunities that encourage viral sharing of branded content</li>
<li>
Capture insights on a brand&rsquo;s social media audience that can be used to optimize various marketing tactics</li>
<li>
Enable monetization of a brand&rsquo;s social media audience by converting fans to customers</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Sales Executive</strong><strong> Description</strong><br />
The primary purpose of the Sales Executive position is to achieve their overall revenue goal for Fan Appz Solutions within their assigned territory.&nbsp; The Sales Executive is responsible for identifying and qualifying opportunities as well as developing and executing strategy.&nbsp; It is expected the Sales Executive be adept at creating and nurturing Executive relationships on their own while positioning the Fan Appz Executive team to assist.</p>
<p>
<strong>Expectations and Tasks</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Directly interact with potential accounts to position the value of Fan Appz solutions</li>
<li>
Prospect accounts as potential customers of Fan Appz Solutions utilizing all available Fan Appz resources</li>
<li>
Pursue professional and personal development to ensure adequate knowledge of the markets and industries Fan Appz serves as well as the products and services Fan Appz provides</li>
<li>
Update on a timely basis the Fan Appz CRM system with accurate customer and pipeline information.</li>
<li>
Timely complete administrative tasks such as expense reports</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Education and Qualifications/ Skills and Competencies</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Requires 5+ years of experience in software sales in a direct account ownership role</li>
<li>
Demonstrated history of achieving sales quota of $2M+ of annual revenue</li>
<li>
Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree Preferred</li>
<li>
Ability to prospect and close deals</li>
<li>
Experience selling software applications to Fortune 1000 Companies and C level executives</li>
<li>
Team player with strong interpersonal&nbsp; and communication skills.</li>
<li>
Excellent negotiating and closing skills with prospects and customers.</li>
<li>
Travel may be needed.<br />
&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p>
Fan Appz does not accept unsolicited headhunter and agency resumes. Fan Appz will not pay fees to any third-party agency or company that does not have a signed agreement with the Company.</p>
]]></description>
